## Status legend

| Symbol | Meaning |
|---|---|
| ⬜ | Not started |
| 🟡 | In progress / partially done |
| ✅ | Done and aligned with PRD |

> `verified-in-codebase?` column: whether actually confirmed in the codebase (not from memory). Fill in `yes (file:line)` / `no` / `⚠️speculation`.

